{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"292fdf0488","title":"关于游泳池建造费由稿费中支出给刘少奇等的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"436873cc03","index":0,"year":1954,"month":4,"day":25,"articleId":"292fdf0488"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"fe663790b0","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"292fdf0488","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。陈，指陈云，当时任中共中央书记处书记、政务院副总理兼财政经济委员会主任。邓，指邓小平，当时任政务院副总理兼财政部部长。罗瑞卿，当时任政务院政治法律委员会副主任兼公安部部长。尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央办公厅主任。汪东兴，当时任中共中央办公厅警卫局局长。"},{"id":"760eca9e33","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"292fdf0488","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指江青1954年4月20日给毛泽东的信。信中对她拉自提议给毛泽东修建游泳池一事作了检讨。"},{"id":"246d125159","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"292fdf0488","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这里是以当时流通的人民币计算的，按中国人民银行1955年3月1日起发行的新人民币折算，合5万元（新币1元等于旧币1万元）。"}],"contents":[{"id":"136f2c02f8","type":"title","text":"关于游泳池建造费由稿费中支出给刘少奇等的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"292fdf0488"},{"id":"fe663790b0","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、陈、邓、罗瑞卿、尚昆、汪东兴诸同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"292fdf0488"},{"id":"760eca9e33","type":"paragraph","text":"江青此信请阅。为补救计，建造费五亿由我的稿费中支出游泳池封闭不用。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"292fdf0488"},{"id":"246d125159","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"292fdf0488"},{"id":"092aa3e074","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年四月廿五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"292fdf0488"}],"page":{"id":"1